spectives, 18(3): 135–46.

W.F.  Stolper  and  P.A.  Samuelson  (1941)  ‘‘Protection  and  Real  Wages,’’  Review  of

Economic Studies 9: 58–73.

The Economist (2006) ‘‘Denmark’s Labor Market: Flexicurity,’’ September 7.
Tobin,  J.  (1975)  ‘‘Keynesian  Models  of  Recession  and  Depression,’’  American  Eco-

nomic Review 65: 195–202.

